## Payment Records - Boleto Payment Method Details

### Response Schema
```json
{
  "payment_method_details": {
    "boleto": {
      "tax_id": "string (required)",
      "fingerprint": "string"
    }
  }
}
```

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| tax_id | string | Yes | The tax ID of the customer |
| fingerprint | string | No | Unique identifier for the bank account |

